item.description:
This year's theme is; "Meet and Greet the Republican Presidential Candidates".

Location: Ctr Strafford, NH on the property of Mr. and Mrs Brian Payne.

Time: 12:00PM to 5:00PM
Food: Hot Dogs, Hamburgers, and a surprise with music to please your ears.
Tickets: $20.00 per person, children under 12 Free

http://www.straffordc...

Contacts for tickets and directions:
Hon. Phyllis Woods, Strafford County Chair (Tel: 603-749-2177)
and/or Hon. Sam A. Cataldo, Picnic Chairman (Tel: 603-589-1089).

Note: The folks in charge of Strafford County will have a display table for Ron at this event and Ron Paul himself will be with us. There will be a straw poll! Please try to buy your tickets in advance.

if anyone is interested in carpooling, they should contact Will at DigitalWarrior@gmail.com
item.name: The Strafford County Annual Republican Picnic
